.TH LOA-EDIT 1 "2026-03-15" "Library Of Alexandria" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
edit \- Edit fields of an item selected by reference
.SH SYNOPSIS
alexandria> edit
.SH DESCRIPTION
.TP
Prompts for the target item reference (ID, ISBN, title, or author/composer) and shows current values.
.TP
Press Enter to keep a value, or type none to clear optional fields.
.TP
You can switch type (Book/SheetMusic), edit shared metadata, and update sheet-music-specific fields in one flow.
.TP
Changes are saved immediately if valid.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
alexandria> edit
